---
title: SuperQuick Sausage and Veggie Tortellini with Blistered Tomatoes and Peas
description: This dish features Italian sausage and delicate tortellini stuffed with rich cheese in a velvety cream sauce. Vibrant peas and blistered cherry tomatoes add a burst of colour and sweetness, and a generous sprinkle of freshly grated Parmesan brings it all home.

